---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Work with us">
  <div class="prose">
    <header>
      <h1>Work with us</h1>
    </header>
    <p>
      We take on a small number of engagements at a time, usually with news
      organizations and the people who fund and support them. The work tends to
      fall into a few buckets: applied AI and data strategy, prototyping and
      product development, and helping newsrooms build the internal capacity to
      do this work themselves.
    </p>
    <p>
      We're most useful when the problem is concrete, the timeline is real,
      and the goal is something a newsroom will actually use.
    </p>
    <p>
      If that sounds like what you need, write us:
      <a href="mailto:hello@localangle.co">hello@localangle.co</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
